Description: SQL toolkit and Object Relational Mapper (Avalan PPA pin)
 SQLAlchemy is the Python SQL toolkit and Object Relational Mapper that
 gives application developers the full power and flexibility of SQL.
 This package is built for the Avalan PPA because Avalan's `tool`
 extras require `SQLAlchemy >= 2.0.43` and Noble ships 1.4.50 -- below
 the 2.x floor. Pinned at 2.0.49, the current upstream 2.0.x stable.
 .
 The optional Cython-built `sqlalchemy.cyextension` modules are
 compiled opportunistically; the package falls back to the pure-Python
 path when an extension is unavailable.
